OL,3,CIFS accuses Labour and Tories of
OL,4,C'conspiracy of silence' over manifestos
OL,6,FMr Johnson said: "They (Labour and
OL,7,FConservatives) have singularly failed
OL,8,Feven to acknowledge some of the most
OL,9,Fimportant issues and choices to have
OL,10,Ffaced us for a very long time."
OL,12,FHe added: "Their proposals on tax,
OL,13,Fbenefits and public service spending
OL,14,Fwould be barely enough to detain us in
OL,15,Fanalysing a modest one-year fiscal
OL,16,Fevent.
OL,18,F"They certainly don't answer the big
OL,19,Fquestions facing us over a five-year
OL,20,Fparliament."
