OL,6,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer and
OL,7,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak have both
OL,8,Frefused to agree with the IFS' analysis
OL,10,FStarmer said that he does not accept
OL,11,Fthe economy "cannot be better than
OL,12,Fwhat it is now", while Sunak insisted
OL,13,Fhis party's tax cuts "can deliver" for
OL,14,Fpeople at "every stage in their lives".
