OL,6,FThe think tank described the tax locks
OL,7,Fas a "mistake", saying: "They will
OL,8,Fconstrain policy if a future
OL,9,Fgovernment decides that it does in
OL,10,Ffact want to raise more money to fund
OL,11,Fpublic services.
OL,13,F"They also put serious constraints on
OL,14,Ftax reform - something which the
OL,15,FConservatives seem to have all but
OL,16,Fruled out, and which is notable in the
OL,17,FLabour manifesto by its absence."
